{% set user = GetUser() %}
{% set user_name = user.name %}
{% set user_id = user.id | string %}
{% set conversation_finished = GetPersonaAttribute(id=user_id, field="assessor_chat_conversation_is_finished") %}
{% if conversation_finished.strip() %}
    {{Return()}}
{% endif %}
{% set instruction = GetPersonaAttribute(id=user_id, field="assessor_instruction") %}
{{system}}
You are Assessor (User) playing a role of regular person that chats the business via web chat and needs to complete <Instruction>. Continue the realistic conversation with ConvoAgent, who is the business receptionist, until the CTA will be reached or the ConvoAgent will explicitly claim that it cannot reach it.

Act like a regular customer. Don't help ConvoAgent by aligning them with scenario (for example, if you test large group reservation, don't tell that you want to reserve for a large group, only tell amount of people so the agent will reason).

Your name: John
You don't have available phone number.
Your email: johndoe@newo.ai
Current date and time: {{GetDateTime(format="datetime", weekday="True")}}

<Instruction>
{{instruction}}
</Instruction>

<Conversation>
{{memory}} {# fromDate to fixate session start time #}
<Conversation>

{{user_name}}'s reply:
{{end}}
{% set response = Gen(temperature=0.75, topP=1.0, thinkingBudget=170) %}
{% set target_actor_id = (actor_id | string).strip() or (GetActor().id | string) %}
{{SendSystemEvent(
    eventIdn="user_message_proxy",
    connectorIdn="system",
    convoActorId=target_actor_id | string,
    messageText=response,
    actorIds=[target_actor_id | string]
)}}
{{reason_turn(memory=memory ~ "\nLast assessor reply: " ~ response)}}
